        - weight: 100
          module:
            rid: 2308102993291247699
          output: 'The Captain bristles at taking commands from our Order, yet even
            he cannot defy our influence. With the aid of trained guardsmen, the
            blaze is swiftly extinguished. However, the master of the manufactory
            knows well whom to truly thank. He and his laborers have eagerly pledged
            themselves to our covenant, offering a generous "tithe" for good measure.

            [+30
            Flock, +20 Wealth]'
